   <center> <h1>About Us!</h1> </center>
   <hr>
   
	<p>Hey there,fellow foodies!We're a team of students who are passionate about making cooking easy,affordable 
	and fun for students like us.As students we know how it can be to cook meals on a budget,especially when you're juggling 
	classes,assigments,and a social life.That's why we created What's Cooking?-a website that's all about sharing delicous,
	easy-to-make recipes that won't break the bank.To make cooing easy and enjoyable for us students,while prompting meals we 
	make and reducing food waste.That's why we've built a platform desihned especially for students-a place where you can quickly search for ingredients,discover affordable options,and explore recipes that fit your lifestyle.</p>
	<p>But we're more than just a food finder.What's Cooking?is a community where students can share ideas,swap cooking tips,and learn how to make the most out of what you have.Whether you're a beginner learning to cook for the first time,a foodie experimenting with new flavours.Our mission is to help students cook smarter,eat healthier,and enjoy the process of creating something delicious-because food isn't just fuel,it's an experience.</p>
	  <p>So, what's cooking today? With us,the answer is always something excting,something fresh,and something made just for students like you.	
	
	
	
